you can do whatever you want.

552
00:56:44,361 --> 00:56:45,516
Sophie.

553
00:56:45,516 --> 00:56:46,936
Sophie, come back!

554
00:56:46,936 --> 00:56:50,337
Sophie!

555
00:58:16,636 --> 00:58:17,496
So.

556
00:58:19,689 --> 00:58:21,056
Are you okay?

557
00:58:47,010 --> 00:58:50,264
I'm sorry for bothering you.

558
00:58:51,374 --> 00:58:53,120
You don't need to apologize.

559
00:58:53,896 --> 00:58:56,801
Honestly, you can bother me anytime.

560
00:58:58,374 --> 00:58:59,621
It's just...

561
00:59:01,302 --> 00:59:03,097
I couldn't imagine...

562
00:59:04,652 --> 00:59:06,832
if I didn't have you...

563
00:59:07,586 --> 00:59:09,904
how I would get through today.

564
00:59:37,989 --> 00:59:39,944
I have a girlfriend now, So.

565
00:59:41,349 --> 00:59:43,251
That doesn't matter.

566
00:59:45,726 --> 00:59:47,435
I can be whatever you want.

567
00:59:49,256 --> 00:59:50,970
As long as I have you.

568
01:00:23,166 --> 01:00:24,746
You're home pretty late.

569
01:00:24,746 --> 01:00:27,123
I was helping my friends clean up the grandstand.

570
01:00:27,598 --> 01:00:29,538
I wasn't going to scold you.

571
01:00:29,942 --> 01:00:34,124
Actually, I'm glad you're finally using the iPad I bought you.

572
01:00:34,423 --> 01:00:36,941
I saw it sitting in your room unopened for so long.

573
01:00:36,942 --> 01:00:39,419
So I bought you a keyboard for it today.

574
01:00:40,979 --> 01:00:44,449
They said it makes typing as fast as on a laptop.

575
01:00:45,044 --> 01:00:48,838
Try connecting it. I didn't even get to test it when I bought it.

576
01:00:48,839 --> 01:00:50,514
To see if it really types that fast.

577
01:00:53,085 --> 01:00:54,580
Dad...

578
01:00:55,881 --> 01:00:58,496
The iPad isn't with me right now.

579
01:01:00,427 --> 01:01:04,753
My close friend really needed money urgently.

580
01:01:04,754 --> 01:01:07,596
And since I wasn't really using it...

581
01:01:08,953 --> 01:01:10,400
I decided...

582
01:01:10,682 --> 01:01:12,470
to sell it.

583
01:01:14,556 --> 01:01:18,935
But once I get the money back, I'll buy a new one for you.

584
01:01:22,811 --> 01:01:25,275
You're exactly like your mother.

585
01:01:25,734 --> 01:01:27,931
Always taking my money to give to other women.

586
01:01:27,932 --> 01:01:31,796
Your mom lied to me countless times.

587
01:01:31,797 --> 01:01:33,655
Sometimes claiming you were sick.

588
01:01:33,656 --> 01:01:35,858
But in the end, she gave the money to another woman.

589
01:01:36,785 --> 01:01:38,713
Are you planning to be a deviant like her?

590
01:01:38,713 --> 01:01:40,091
What the hell are you talking about?

591
01:01:40,341 --> 01:01:41,463
Mom isn't like that.

592
01:01:41,463 --> 01:01:42,950
She is exactly like that.

593
01:01:43,470 --> 01:01:45,527
The reason you had to come live with me...

594
01:01:45,940 --> 01:01:47,337
is because your mom...

595
01:01:48,052 --> 01:01:49,519
was going to take a million baht

596
01:01:49,807 --> 01:01:52,175
to open a cafe for that Pim woman.

597
01:01:52,176 --> 01:01:55,543
That's not true! Mom was afraid the loan sharks would hurt me.

598
01:01:55,544 --> 01:01:57,541
Then hear it from her yourself.

599
01:02:00,855 --> 01:02:04,153
Haven't you told her about that one million baht yet?

600
01:02:04,812 --> 01:02:08,658
I did, but your daughter just wouldn't believe it.

601
01:02:09,966 --> 01:02:11,706
Well, she caused some trouble.

602
01:02:12,588 --> 01:02:16,609
Who in their right mind sells the iPad I bought for them?

603
01:02:16,972 --> 01:02:18,748
And says they gave the money to a friend.

604
01:02:20,253 --> 01:02:22,096
She's just like you.

605
01:02:23,025 --> 01:02:25,193
The apple doesn't fall far from the tree.

606
01:02:28,945 --> 01:02:31,800
Make sure you explain that million baht to her clearly.

607
01:02:33,932 --> 01:02:36,436
And go get my iPad back.

608
01:03:53,623 --> 01:03:55,293
Long time no see.

609
01:03:56,199 --> 01:03:57,593
Visiting the school?

610
01:03:59,545 --> 01:04:01,194
Oh, actually...

611
01:04:02,070 --> 01:04:04,063
I'm the new guidance counselor here.

612
01:04:07,263 --> 01:04:10,104
Someone from the central board whispered to me that

613
01:04:10,662 --> 01:04:13,941
the inspector will come disguised as the new guidance counselor.

614
01:04:15,938 --> 01:04:19,185
And what about you, Nalin? What are you doing here?

615
01:04:20,727 --> 01:04:22,936
I'm a French teacher.

616
01:04:22,937 --> 01:04:24,280
Really?

617
01:04:24,281 --> 01:04:28,159
That means we'll get to see each other often then.

618
01:04:33,870 --> 01:04:35,064
Actually,

619
01:04:35,825 --> 01:04:38,520
I had something I wanted to reach out to you about.

620
01:04:39,073 --> 01:04:41,030
I just couldn't find the right time.

621
01:04:43,674 --> 01:04:45,369
About your wedding, right?

622
01:04:48,076 --> 01:04:49,319
You knew?

623
01:04:51,117 --> 01:04:52,143
Yeah.

624
01:04:54,056 --> 01:04:55,866
I heard it from a friend.

625
01:04:57,349 --> 01:04:58,943
Congratulations, Mink.

626
01:04:59,699 --> 01:05:01,472
Finally, here...

627
01:05:01,667 --> 01:05:04,415
women can actually marry women now.

628
01:05:04,570 --> 01:05:06,348
The law passed faster than expected, huh?

629
01:05:10,288 --> 01:05:11,301
Yeah.

630
01:05:11,994 --> 01:05:15,223
I thought I'd be the one getting married before you.

631
01:05:15,224 --> 01:05:18,111
But it turns out you beat me to it.

632
01:05:20,576 --> 01:05:22,575
I'm really happy for you, Mink.

633
01:05:32,170 --> 01:05:34,396
But I'd really love for you to come to the wedding.

634
01:05:34,835 --> 01:05:36,610
During our high school years,

635
01:05:37,049 --> 01:05:39,369
besides a few close friends,

636
01:05:39,995 --> 01:05:41,470
it was just you...

637
01:05:41,471 --> 01:05:44,430
who I felt was truly important in my life.

638
01:05:51,254 --> 01:05:52,554
But...

639
01:05:52,742 --> 01:05:54,548
if it makes you uncomfortable,

640
01:05:55,476 --> 01:05:57,012
that's completely fine.

641
01:05:57,526 --> 01:05:58,745
I understand.

642
01:06:01,335 --> 01:06:02,610
Thank you.

643
01:06:03,887 --> 01:06:04,934
I'll...

644
01:06:05,870 --> 01:06:07,616
think about it.

645
01:06:18,273 --> 01:06:19,919
This place has changed a lot.

646
01:06:19,920 --> 01:06:22,949
If you need anything, just ask, new teacher.

647
01:06:25,653 --> 01:06:29,625
Since you started teaching here, have there been any issues?

648
01:06:30,595 --> 01:06:33,906
Are kids these days still like we were?

649
01:06:34,313 --> 01:06:37,176
Like secretly crushing on each other.

650
01:06:37,629 --> 01:06:39,504
Secretly doing things they shouldn't.

651
01:06:40,282 --> 01:06:42,788
Or rebelling against the school rules like we did?

652
01:06:55,188 --> 01:06:56,881
There's nothing like that here.

653
01:07:01,375 --> 01:07:02,616
Because here...

654
01:07:02,616 --> 01:07:03,562
[Hello, YUMIVERSE.]

655
01:07:03,563 --> 01:07:05,713
[We met the other day, Earn.]
we teach all of our students...

656
01:07:08,573 --> 01:07:11,096
[Which foundations are you raising funds for this month?
I want to help.]

657
01:07:22,975 --> 01:07:24,782
[Will you be my girlfriend?]

658
01:07:38,206 --> 01:07:39,946
to be well-behaved.

659
01:07:43,209 --> 01:07:46,027
Hello, Earn? I think I like you.

660
01:07:46,028 --> 01:07:48,460
Why are you only telling me this now, Belle?

661
01:07:53,875 --> 01:07:55,888
All this time, you tricked me into helping you scam money?

662
01:07:55,889 --> 01:07:58,429
Tell me! Speak up! My mom helped you...

663
01:07:58,430 --> 01:08:01,193
I went out of my way to help you too. Why are you so selfish?

664
01:08:01,194 --> 01:08:02,146
Mink.

